product_name: freshLotus Youth Preserve Line & Texture Smoothing Moisturizer
summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsSustainable PackagingGive BackFresh's Lotus Youth Preserve Line & Texture Smoothing Moisturizer is a lightweight antioxidant moisturizer that helps smooth texture & the look of fine lines while boosting hydration for radiant, youthful-looking skin.
details: DetailsBenefitsSmoothes texture & the look of fine linesBoosts radiance for a youthful lookDelivers 24hr hydration** & preps for makeup**instrumental test, 30 subjectsKey IngredientsSuper Lotus smoothes lines & helps to boost radianceStar fruit leaf extract smoothes while helping to reduce visible wrinklesPolyglutamic acid works to lock in moisture & comfortVitamin E helps protect & sootheResearch ResultsClinically proven to smooth texture & fine lines*+19% radiance observed**97% agreed it created a smooth canvas for makeup***+14% smoother skin after 1 application****24hr hydration****+17% smoother skin observed after 4 weeks***clinical assessment by dermatologist, 30 subjects, 4 weeks**self-assessment by scoring, 30 subjects, 4 weeks***self-assessment, 104 subjects, 4 weeks****instrumental test, 30 subjectsItem 2617054How To UseApply to clean skin twice a day, morning and night.IngredientsAqua (water), Glycerin, Propylene Glycol Dicaprylate/dicaprate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Pentylene Glycol, Caprylic/capric Triglyceride, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, C10-18 Triglycerides, Betaine, Polyglycerin-3, Nelumbo Nucifera Extract, Citrus Limon (lemon) Peel Oil, Averrhoa Carambola Leaf Extract, Cucumis Sativus (cucumber) Fruit Extract, Helianthus Annuus (sunflower) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Cetearyl Glucoside, Sorbitol, Caprylyl Glycol, Potassium Cetyl Phosphate, Behenyl Alcohol, Carbomer, Silica, Sodium Pca, Cetyl Alcohol, Stearyl Alcohol, Butylene Glycol, Pentaerythrityl Tetraisostearate, Sodium Hydroxide, Xanthan Gum, Adenosine, Sodium Polyglutamate, Sodium Phytate, Propanediol, Caramel, Chlorphenesin, Sodium Metabisulfite, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Limonene, Citral \<18907\>.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Apply to clean skin twice a day, morning and night.

reviews.headline: Great moisturizer
reviews.comments: I have oily skin but like an anti aging moisturizer at night. This is great. Its thick but my skin absorbs it very well.

reviews.headline: Light and Wonderful
reviews.comments: This moisturizer is light, absorbs well and has clean ingredients.

reviews.headline: So expensive
reviews.comments: This moisturizer was not worth the money. Only used it for a week. Didn't noticed any difference. I used it at night, I experienced the burning sensation on my bare and clean face. And I don't even have sensitive skin. I would not repurchase.

reviews.headline: beautiful skin
reviews.comments: i use this moisturizer before applying makeup and my makeup looks amazing. it gives my face a beautiful smooth glow. I wish they made a bigger size, I go thru it very fast. worth every penny

reviews.headline: Recipe for glass skin!
reviews.comments: I got this during Ulta's 21 days of beauty sale and it's so good! I use it after my Peach & Lily glass skin serum and all my texture and redness is gone. Helps makeup go on so well!

reviews.headline: Wouldn't buy
reviews.comments: I really wanted this to work for my redness, but it just made my skin redder! I love fresh but this product just wasn't for me. It also burned around my lip area. Would not recommend for sensitive skin.

reviews.headline: Drying üò≠
reviews.comments: I'm 28 yrs old w/ extremely dry skin, and I'm just starting to see my 11's. I bought this moisturizer 2 weeks ago bc the packaging boasted anti-aging properties & hydration. This product did NOT add any hydration to my skin & it actually emphasized the the 11's I was trying to plump up. I was super disappointed & I'll most likely go back to the Biossance or Cosrx Snail Mucin moisturizers bc they actually work!

reviews.headline: My second bottle
reviews.comments: I love the texture and how moist the cream is on my clean

reviews.headline: It burns and makes my skin look red
reviews.comments: Product is great, but just not for me. I'm not sure if product is not a match with my toner or retinol but when applying it gives me a burn sensation and I look red but then it goes away. Product didn't work for me. It's probably a match for other type of skin but not with mine.

reviews.headline: Had skin reaction
reviews.comments: Definitely try a swatch of this product in store before you buy. I do not have sensitive skin but I reacted to this product within like a minute of trying it in Ulta. So glad I tried before I buyed. The texture of the product was nice though and smelled good so if your skin doesn't react I'm sure its a great product.

reviews.headline: Bring back old formula
reviews.comments: My makeup used to blend beautifully over this and feel so luxe. New formula broke that. So disappointing. Why break something that has awesome reviews‚Ä¶it's so hard to get customers to come back after leaving.

reviews.headline: Changed formula
reviews.comments: I had a sample that I used and loved, so I decided to buy it. Well, this must have been an old sample since I saw other comments about their formula change. This version made me break out in hives and was very itchy. Have to return. So sad because the old version was awesome.

reviews.headline: Love it, will buy it again
reviews.comments: I really like this! I am out of my first jar and will be buying another one this week! Try it! It's not greasy and has a very nice feel!

reviews.headline: Don't like
reviews.comments: I wanted to try something different and this just wasn't for me.  It's very greasy and doesn't absorb and it made me itch terribly

reviews.headline: This product works on fine lines
reviews.comments:
I'd give it 5 stars if the price went a bit lower. I aways have to wait for a coupon to come, its expensive for a bit over an ounce. I've been wearing this for a good 5 years and when i run out, my face shows! It leaves my face looking younger , pores aren't as big, fine lines are gone, and my face is so smooth. I have combination skin.I can tell the recipe has changed I think the quality went down a bit , but still good results.  Please bring the price down

-a faithful customer-

reviews.headline: Sensitive skin follower (don't have sensitive skin)
reviews.comments: I tend to avoid creams that have fragrence in this and this one tends to sting over cuts & dry skin in very fresh states. Other than that I love the feeling of the lotion once applies (I have a mini fridge for my cream) but I just don't appreciate that feeling around sensitive skin cells.

reviews.headline: New formula is a sad No
reviews.comments: I am so disappointed in the formula change :( I ordered a new jar and knew immediately after rubbing it on that something was off. It's almost soapy and doesn't seem to rub in like before. It leaves a bit of white residue too. I've been loyal to this moisturizer for so many years. My skin is not doing well and I'm worried I've developed a bit of an allergic reaction which is actually how I originally came to find this moisturizer. I am so saddened to have to now search for another moisturizer when my skin doesn't do well with most creams. This used to feel luxurious and almost silky. Not anymore!

reviews.headline: This feels so good !
reviews.comments: The cloud-like texture and hydrating feel of this makes the youth preserve moisturizer my go-to for perfect daytime moisture that lasts until it's night routine time

faceoff_positive.comments: I received this product complimentary from Fresh. This cream is absolutely wonderful. It is rich and moisturizing and leaves my skin so hydrated and absolutely radiant. It soaks right in and made my mature skin look wonderful. I skipped my foundation today because my skin looked so good!
